     Hello, demofreaks worldwide!  This little info file that accompanies the
fine production you just downloaded is the Xylem Information Packet version
1.1.  While perhaps not being _quite_ as important as it sounds, it will
(hopefully) provide you with all the information about the demo group Xylem
that you ever wanted to know.  If you don't know much about demos then this
file probably won't help you much.  We'd suggest finding yourself a copy of
the PC Demos FAQ by Hornet, which contains alot of informative text to help
newbies get into the scene.
     Xylem's primary purpose, of course, is to make all of it's members really
rich and powerful and famous and to take over the world.  Until we figure out
how to do that, however, we plan to release alot of these fun things called
demos, as well as some cool tunes, nice artwork and helpful utilities.  So
give this file a looksee.  Maybe you'll even find something useful in here.


