 ˙+*˛È∞±≤€               IV.  Finding Our Stuff               €≤±∞È˛*+˙

     Currently, there are only two places that we know you can get all of our
productions on.  If you have Internet access, FTP to ftp.cdrom.com and look
in the directory /pub/demos.  You'll find all our stuff there, as well as
alot of other group's productions as well.
     OR if you're REALLY cool, call our World Headquarters, Digital Entropy
BBS, at 1-703-549-6982.  All Xylem releases are available for download.  We
also have over 300 Megs of demos and mods as well as the Freedom CD online
and several demo-oriented message subs.  Long distance callers are exempt from
the transfer ratio, and known demo sceners are granted more time a day.  So
give us a call!
     We are currently looking for some distro sites worldwide, so if you are
a SysOp of a demo-oriented board and are interested in distributing our files
please contact us.  We REQUIRE three things:
     1.) Your board MUST be demo-oriented, no general-interest boards, please.
     2.) You must be willing to create a file directory/conference on your
         board called "Xylem Distribution Site" or something similar and to
         place ALL of our releases in it.
     3.) You must have access to Internet mail and FTP, OR call Digital Entropy
         AT LEAST once a month to obtain our new releases.
     We'll probably also want to know stuff like your name, other groups you
are affiliated with, number of users on your system, etc.  Email Loki
(radams@mail.erols.com) or call Digital Entropy to get in touch with us.
     If you maintain an Internet FTP site with demo directories on it, contact
us about becoming an internet distribution site.
     So what's in it for you?  Here are the benefits:
     1.) You get to obtain all our new releases before anybody else does.
     2.) You get to put us in your long list of distro sites :).
     3.) We'll put your BBS name and number or FTP site address in all of our
         future releases.
     Sound good?  I thought so too!  Give us an email today!


